data.description: Adorable, well-maintained ranch with an inviting open floor plan and a bay window that fills the spacious living room in natural light. This charming home boasts a recently updated bathroom, oak kitchen cabinets, central air, and more. The property is being sold in its current condition, and the city inspection report is readily available for your review.
